import { Box, Button, TextField, Typography } from "@mui/material";

const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      display="flex"
      justifyContent="center"
      sx={{ width: "100%", boxSizing: "border-box" }}
    >
      <Box
        display="flex"
        flexDirection="column"
        justifyContent="center"
        width="500px"
        height="700px"
        sx={{ border: "1px solid" }}
      >
        <Box sx={{ border: "1px solid" }}>로고</Box>
        <Box component="form" sx={{ border: "1px solid" }}>
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="email"
            label="email"
            name="email"
            autoComplete="id"
            autoFocus
          />
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            name="password"
            label="Password"
            type="password"
            id="password"
            autoComplete="current-password"
          />
          <Button
            type="submit"
            fullWidth
            sx={{
              mt: 3,
              mb: 2,
              borderRadius: 0,
              bgcolor: "#37b3a8",
              color: "white",
              ":hover": { backgroundColor: "#37b3a8" },
              textTransform: "none",
            }}
          >
            Log In
          </Button>
        </Box>
        <Box pt={3} sx={{ border: "1px solid" }}>
          <Typography>Sign Up</Typography>
        </Box>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Login;
